snippet.title: Mauga Origin Story | Overwatch 2 | BlizzCon 2023
snippet.description:
Introducing the one and only, Mauga.

He’s spent his whole life fighting. Now he’s ready to have some fun.

Hop into Overwatch 2 Nov 3-5 to play him in a limited-time free trial today
_
